title: RARE 80s Post-Punk Dark Wave -Trance Logic (2 albums)
description:
TRANCE LOGIC was a Post-Punk Dark Wave band, formed in the US during the mid 1980s. They recorded 3 albums: Cathedral Of Love, 3-fold Lotus and Execution Revolution. All albums have been out of print since the early 1990s. I will make a torrent for the 3-fold Lotus EP if enough of you request it.

Members:

October - vocals
David Lootz - bass, backing vocals (some lead vocals on Cathedral Of Love album)
Gary "the hypnotist" Shefler - guitar
Eddie The Drummer - drums, backing vocals

EXTREMELY RARE and very cool music from the 1980s.  

Please SEED to at least a 1:1 ratio. In other words, keep this torrent alive by giving back 100% of what you take from others. :) 

Enjoy!
